acme.validation.shortText.message  	= Must have from 1 to 50 characters.
acme.validation.flightNumber.message = The flight number must have exactly three uppercase letters followed by four digits (example: ABC1234).
acme.validation.employeeCode.format.message=The employee code must start with 2 or 3 uppercase letters followed by 6 digits.
acme.validation.employeeCode.unique.message = The employee code must be unique.
acme.validation.employeeCode.initials.message=The employee code must begin with your initials extracted from your full name.
acme.validation.draftMode.message = Validation cannot proceed while the claim is in draft mode.
acme.validation.confirmation.message.update = The claim cannot be updated while it is in draft mode.
acme.validation.trackinglog.no-trackinglogs = No tracking logs found.
acme.validation.trackinglog.status.not-pending = The status cannot be PENDING when the resolution percentage is 100%.
acme.validation.trackinglog.status.pending-required = The status must be PENDING when the resolution percentage is less than 100%.
acme.validation.trackinglog.resolution.incorrect = The resolution field is incorrect based on the current status.
acme.validation.trackinglog.resolution.monotony = The resolution percentage must be monotonically increasing.

